game: Ocarina of Time but it's just Master Quest Water Temple

ootbijmqwt-2.0.description:
- Updates Ocarina of Time but it's just Master Quest Water Temple to be compatible with the latest versions of Archipelago.
- Queen Gohma removed as a boss option: it is not logically beatable due to no repeatable Deku Nut sources, therefore it was not possible to successfully generate with this option chosen.
- The `Market 10 Big Poes` check, when applicable, will now only require one Big Poe instead of four, and the item pool will have only one.
- `LH Adult Fishing`, when applicable, logically requires access to the Market Guard House, to ensure there is a repeatable source of rupees.
ootbijmqwt-2.0.title: Ocarina of Time but it's just Master Quest Water Temple v2.0

ootbijmqwt-v2.1.description:
- Fix to ensure if everyone is playing Burger King start and panic method is not `start_inventory`, it will force one player into Guard House start.
- Iron Boots start + OHKO Deadly Bonks will start you with Nayru's Love and a Magic Meter. Good luck!
- Various minor code fixes.
ootbijmqwt-v2.1.title: Ocarina of Time but it's just Master Quest Water Temple v2.1

v1.0.description:
Ocarina of Time but it's just Master Quest Water Temple v1.0

Differences from initial public game:
* `burger_king_start` option changed to `start_mode`, with a new option to start inside the Water Temple but with Iron Boots.
* `max_health` option to specify the maximum possible hearts obtainable
v1.0.title: Ocarina of Time but it's just Master Quest Water Temple v1.0

v1.1.description: Overrides OoT hint entrance information. Hints for locations that require song warps will now tell you which warp song will take you to them.
v1.1.title: Ocarina of Time but it's just Master Quest Water Temple v1.1

v1.2.title: Ocarina of Time but it's just Master Quest Water Temple v1.2

v1.3.description: Fixes crashes with Minimal Accessibility and Water Temple MQ North Basement GS without Small Key logic trick.
v1.3.title: Ocarina of Time but it's just Master Quest Water Temple v1.3

v1.4.description:
- Adds a new "boss" option to select which boss you'll encounter beyond the Water Temple boss key door.
- Many items that were previously marked as filler or useful are now advancement items again, as they are relevant to certain bosses that could now be fought.
- If start mode is "guard house" and shuffle warp songs is off, walking out of the skulltula house will now return you to the guard house, as it was previously impossible to return to under these conditions
v1.4.title: Ocarina of Time but it's just Master Quest Water Temple v1.4

v1.4.1.description: - Adds Queen Gohma as a boss option
v1.4.1.title: Ocarina of Time but it's just Master Quest Water Temple v1.4.1

v1.5.description:
- Adds two logic settings for bosses that were added as options in v1.4.
- Fixes the "Water Temple MQ Central Pillar with Fire Arrows" logic setting, which crashed generation if turned on.
v1.5.title: Ocarina of Time but it's just Master Quest Water Temple v1.5
